{"tid":1108403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨遊澳患急性敗血症 割膽保命","createTime":"2019-04-16T02:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T01:01:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":818,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6d6e1a7950236d136a3b622850966cc891ff93","tid":1108403,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4240541-%e3%80%90kelly-online%e3%80%91fit%e9%a6%ac%e9%81%8a%e6%be%b3%e5%89%b2%e8%86%bd%e4%bf%9d%e5%91%bd-%e6%ad%bb%e9%81%8e%e7%bf%bb%e7%94%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4240541-%25e3%2580%2590kelly-online%25e3%2580%2591fit%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%2581%258a%25e6%25be%25b3%25e5%2589%25b2%25e8%2586%25bd%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%2591%25bd-%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e9%2581%258e%25e7%25bf%25bb%25e7%2594%259f&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=732da662\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4240541-%e3%80%90kelly-online%e3%80%91fit%e9%a6%ac%e9%81%8a%e6%be%b3%e5%89%b2%e8%86%bd%e4%bf%9d%e5%91%bd-%e6%ad%bb%e9%81%8e%e7%bf%bb%e7%94%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/daily/article/20190412/20653994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%25B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20653994&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5a1a6bcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%25B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F20653994&h=444d8037\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/daily/article/20190412/20653994</a><br />\n馬時亨遊澳割膽保命。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n他此次的經歷，可以是命懸一綫，十分驚險。據說人稱「Fit馬」的馬時亨最初只是有一點點不舒服，以為休息一下就沒事，但越來越不舒服，他的女婿是醫生，便馬上帶他去醫院檢查，院內醫生檢查了一圈，也查不到什麼嚴重問題，所以并沒有要求他馬上留院。<br />\n<br />\n他以為休息一下就沒事，但當晚身體狀況急速轉壞，極度不適，還發高燒，女婿見到情況不妙，立刻再送他去醫院，一量血壓，大家都大吃一驚，原來上壓低至50，心跳卻達140，情況極之危急。醫生立刻幫她做詳細檢查，終於發現他是膽發炎，細菌擴散入侵血管，形成敗血症，如果不制止，會有生命危險。醫生當機立斷，馬上安排手術，將整個膽切除。幸好手術成功，細菌沒有再蔓延，他在醫院留院一個禮拜就康復，可以說是死裡逃生。<br />\n<br />\n事後他回想這件事，覺得自己十分幸運，因為假如在長途飛機上病發，要拖十幾小時才能做手術，他絕對有可能一命嗚呼。假如當時在落後國家，沒有好像澳洲一樣的醫療水平，同樣很麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n他出院後收到賬單，一看嚇一跳，大呼「這麼便宜亅，原來留院加手術只收了一萬幾美金，其中手術費僅收二千四百澳元（約一萬三千港元）。如果同樣的情況在香港手術，可能動輒幾十萬。"},{"pid":"8ae1cf2fa9e1fc2dc41f2c534f0926bfa788746e","tid":1108403,"uid":228963,"like":431,"dislike":2,"score":429,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e96cc96536af213eb4cbf257ae7c667bc613904c","tid":1108403,"uid":5159,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:51:40.000Z","msg":"終於都換人?"},{"pid":"85051f12683280a6ccb58fb201a0bead69f3f9db","tid":1108403,"uid":180040,"like":504,"dislike":0,"score":504,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVsRNFb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVsRNFb.gif&h=2e5052b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AyUEb6W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAyUEb6W.gif&h=09a65a00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90634868161ebf70104b6db0d78d737de141b942","tid":1108403,"uid":113626,"like":200,"dislike":0,"score":200,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"比白人救返你一命算好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780b650aa4b62f339d98ed082cb5d6852d827a5e","tid":1108403,"uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n他出院後收到賬單，一看嚇一跳，大呼「這麼便宜亅，原來留院加手術只收了一萬幾美金，其中手術費僅收二千四百澳元（約一萬三千港元）。如果同樣的情況在香港手術，可能動輒幾十萬。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\